<item>
            <title>[LU-10115] Backport appropriate patches to 2.8 FE for RHEL 7.4</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10115</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We need to update systems to RHEL 7.4, which run Lustre 2.8.&#160; This includes both clients and servers.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please backport the appropriate patches to the 2.8 FE branch, so that we can cherry-pick them and build working Lustre packages for&#160;those environments.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Build Version: 2.8.0_12.chaos &lt;br/&gt;
See &lt;a href=&quot;ssh://review.whamcloud.com/fs/lustre-release-fe-llnl&quot;&gt;ssh://review.whamcloud.com/fs/lustre-release-fe-llnl&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br/&gt;
RHEL 7.4 kernel&lt;br/&gt;
osd-zfs and osd-ldiskfs&lt;br/&gt;
MLX-4, MLX-5, and OPA interfaces&lt;br/&gt;
DNE phase 1 (remote dirs)</environment>
